casebody.data:
Before Bookstaver, Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

David M. Koehler, Appellant, v. John J. Gorman, as Sheriff, etc., Respondent. C. Goldzier, for appellant. Wm. E. Stillings, for respondent. Appeal from judgment of the City Court.

Judgment reversed, new trial ordered, with costs to appellants to abide the event.
